name: Westgold Resources Limited Ordinary shares
longDescription: Westgold Resources Limited is an innovative and growth-oriented, Western Australian gold miner. With more than 1,300km2 of tenure, Westgold is the dominant gold miner in the Murchison and Bryah regions of Western Australia and, uniquely amongst peers, an owner-operator of all of its underground mines. With a new team, increasing operational delivery, no debt and a strong balance sheet, Westgold is well positioned for growth.
